# Data & artifacts (regenerable, large — never commit)
# Anchored with a leading slash so they only match the artifact dirs at the
# my_implementation root — a bare `data/` also matched the source package
# `src/monowad/data/`, silently un-tracking it.
/data/
outputs/
/wandb/
/checkpoints/
*.h5
*.pkl
*.npy
*.png
*.pth
*.ckpt

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
.pytest_cache/

# Env
.env
